00:13:01.839 --> 00:13:04.870
'Filled with so-called asylum seekers who

00:13:04.870 --> 00:13:04.880
repay

00:13:04.880 --> 00:13:06.629
kindness. And that's what they

00:13:06.639 --> 00:13:09.829
did. They repaid kindness with crime.

00:13:09.839 --> 00:13:11.670
It's time to end the failed experiment

00:13:11.680 --> 00:13:14.069
of open borders. You have to end it now.

00:13:14.079 --> 00:13:16.629
See, I can tell you, I'm really good at

00:13:16.639 --> 00:13:18.790
this stuff. Your countries are going to

00:13:18.800 --> 00:13:20.790
hell.

00:13:20.800 --> 00:13:23.030
In America, we've taken bold action to

00:13:23.040 --> 00:13:24.949
swiftly shut down uncontrolled

00:13:24.959 --> 00:13:27.590
migration. Once we started detaining and

00:13:27.600 --> 00:13:29.269
deporting everyone who crossed the

00:13:29.279 --> 00:13:31.990
border and removing illegal aliens from

00:13:32.000 --> 00:13:33.829
the United States, they simply stopped

00:13:33.839 --> 00:13:35.190
coming. They're not coming anymore.

00:13:35.200 --> 00:13:36.150
We're getting a lot of credit, but

00:13:36.160 --> 00:13:40.550
they're not coming

00:13:40.550 --> 00:13:40.560
anymore.'He's

00:13:40.560 --> 00:13:43.509
just funny. I think it's funny. You

00:13:43.519 --> 00:13:45.269
know, when you don't

00:13:45.279 --> 00:13:46.710
have a teleprompter, you start just

00:13:46.720 --> 00:13:48.389
talking. He's just funny. I mean, I

00:13:48.399 --> 00:13:49.509
don't know. Some of you might not think

00:13:49.519 --> 00:13:51.509
that's funny, but I think it's funny.

00:13:51.519 --> 00:13:53.430
But

00:13:53.440 --> 00:13:56.629
we saw him stand behind Israel today. We

00:13:56.639 --> 00:13:59.910
saw him stand by what I knew in my

00:13:59.920 --> 00:14:02.310
spirit that he would do, warning

00:14:02.320 --> 00:14:04.870
the other people and them

00:14:04.880 --> 00:14:07.189
saying, 'We need to have peace

00:14:07.199 --> 00:14:09.430
in Gaza. We need to have peace in these

00:14:09.430 --> 00:14:09.440
areas.'But

00:14:09.440 --> 00:14:11.509
he's like, 'We need

00:14:11.519 --> 00:14:14.230
to release the hostages that they've

00:14:14.240 --> 00:14:16.310
been holding for over—going on, I don't

00:14:16.320 --> 00:14:18.629
know, is this three years? Two, three

00:14:18.639 --> 00:14:20.310
years.'It's

00:14:20.320 --> 00:14:23.110
ridiculous. These men and women

00:14:23.110 --> 00:14:23.120
who

00:14:23.120 --> 00:14:25.189
are still being held—I think he

00:14:25.199 --> 00:14:27.590
said twelve of them—they should be with

00:14:27.600 --> 00:14:30.230
their families in the process of

00:14:30.240 --> 00:14:32.150
peace. And then they

00:14:32.160 --> 00:14:35.750
asked, 'Should NATO countries

00:14:35.760 --> 00:14:39.269
shoot down Russian planes or

00:14:39.279 --> 00:14:41.590
whatever if they cross over into areas

00:14:41.600 --> 00:14:44.230
they shouldn't?'And he said,

00:14:44.230 --> 00:14:44.240
'Yes.'So,

00:14:44.240 --> 00:14:46.310
you know, there's a lot of escalation

00:14:46.320 --> 00:14:48.790
there. What I told you I feel will

00:14:48.800 --> 00:14:51.509
turn into World War III in the days

00:14:51.519 --> 00:14:54.150
ahead. I pray that it does not. I

00:14:54.160 --> 00:14:55.990
pray for peace over the whole world. But

00:14:56.000 --> 00:14:58.150
we know what the Bible says, that there

00:14:58.150 --> 00:14:58.160
will

00:14:58.160 --> 00:15:00.230
be escalations of wars and

00:15:00.240 --> 00:15:02.470
rumors of wars. There will be plagues,

00:15:02.470 --> 00:15:02.480
pestilences,

00:15:02.480 --> 00:15:04.069
and

00:15:04.079 --> 00:15:06.389
all these things. But

00:15:06.399 --> 00:15:09.670
this is the beginning of sorrows,

00:15:09.680 --> 00:15:12.310
and the Lord told us this was coming.

00:15:12.320 --> 00:15:14.949
So, we're seeing it unfold. But as we

00:15:14.959 --> 00:15:17.189
prayed last night, does anybody remember

00:15:17.199 --> 00:15:20.389
what was said in last night's prayer

00:15:20.399 --> 00:15:21.910
time

00:15:21.920 --> 00:15:24.790
that was glorious? I'll go right into

00:15:24.800 --> 00:15:26.069
that real quick, and we'll talk about

00:15:26.079 --> 00:15:27.269
some other things and pray for a

00:15:27.279 --> 00:15:29.750
little bit.

00:15:29.760 --> 00:15:33.509
Last night, I saw the cloud,

00:15:33.519 --> 00:15:36.150
and the cloud started to build. It was

00:15:36.160 --> 00:15:40.069
the size of a car at the time when I

00:15:40.079 --> 00:15:42.710
first saw it on

00:15:42.720 --> 00:15:46.230
the edge of heaven. I could see it

00:15:46.230 --> 00:15:46.240
start

00:15:46.240 --> 00:15:48.629
to grow,

00:15:48.639 --> 00:15:51.110
and the cloud began to grow with

00:15:51.120 --> 00:15:54.069
such intensity and so quickly that it

00:15:54.079 --> 00:15:56.949
started to fill up the whole

00:15:56.959 --> 00:16:00.069
area of the vision. It looked like a

00:16:00.079 --> 00:16:02.389
raincloud, but it got

00:16:02.399 --> 00:16:05.509
larger and larger and larger.

00:16:05.519 --> 00:16:07.350
I could see it, and it was taking

00:16:07.360 --> 00:16:11.670
shape. All of a sudden,

00:16:11.680 --> 00:16:15.350
drops of rain started to fall,

00:16:15.360 --> 00:16:17.910
and you could see the rain falling in

00:16:17.920 --> 00:16:21.430
the rays of the light coming from behind

00:16:21.440 --> 00:16:25.030
the cloud. I could see the rain

00:16:25.040 --> 00:16:27.189
begin to fall,

00:16:29.199 --> 00:16:32.710
just starting to sprinkle.

00:16:32.720 --> 00:16:37.110
But I heard the sound of an abundance of

00:16:37.120 --> 00:16:41.670
rain upon the nations of this earth.

00:16:41.680 --> 00:16:44.389
And all of a sudden, I could hear the

00:16:44.399 --> 00:16:46.230
rain in the spirit realm, and you could

00:16:46.240 --> 00:16:48.230
smell it. You could feel the rain

00:16:48.240 --> 00:16:51.030
falling upon me. I could feel it as it

00:16:51.040 --> 00:16:54.550
was raining. And He said, 'I looked at

00:16:54.560 --> 00:16:57.430
Africa, and I could see the African

00:16:57.440 --> 00:17:01.269
people. They were in tribal

00:17:01.279 --> 00:17:03.829
outfits, and they had

00:17:03.839 --> 00:17:05.669
their hands

00:17:05.669 --> 00:17:05.679
raised,

00:17:05.679 --> 00:17:08.470
worshiping the Lord.'And some

00:17:08.480 --> 00:17:11.590
of them were twirling. And as they were

00:17:11.600 --> 00:17:16.150
doing that, I saw the rain pouring down

00:17:16.160 --> 00:17:19.189
on them in Africa as they were

00:17:19.199 --> 00:17:21.590
worshiping. I could see

00:17:21.600 --> 00:17:24.710
the water running down their faces and

00:17:24.720 --> 00:17:27.029
all down their arms and their bodies.

00:17:27.039 --> 00:17:29.350
And I could see the rain of the Holy

00:17:29.360 --> 00:17:31.669
Spirit raining down on them. It was

00:17:31.679 --> 00:17:33.350
coming. It was in their mouth; it was on

00:17:33.360 --> 00:17:35.350
their lips. And I could see the rain,

00:17:35.360 --> 00:17:38.310
and they were saturated with the

00:17:38.320 --> 00:17:41.669
presence and the glory of the Lord. And

00:17:41.679 --> 00:17:45.350
their skin began to shine as the glory

00:17:45.360 --> 00:17:47.270
was on their faces and the rain was

00:17:47.280 --> 00:17:50.470
there. And I heard the Spirit of the

00:17:50.480 --> 00:17:54.230
Lord say, 'This is the former and the

00:17:54.240 --> 00:17:56.870
latter rain together, and another wave

00:17:56.880 --> 00:17:59.510
of the glory is coming upon

00:17:59.520 --> 00:18:01.909
the nations of the earth.'I saw then

00:18:01.919 --> 00:18:04.549
the rain begin to spread throughout

00:18:04.559 --> 00:18:07.990
everywhere: Asia, South America,

00:18:08.000 --> 00:18:12.070
America, and it was glorious.

00:18:12.080 --> 00:18:13.990
And I could hear the rain. And that's

00:18:14.000 --> 00:18:16.470
whenever I kept hearing Him say, 'Can these

00:18:16.480 --> 00:18:18.789
bones live?

00:18:18.799 --> 00:18:22.630
Can the dry bones of

00:18:22.630 --> 00:18:22.640
the

00:18:22.640 --> 00:18:27.350
spiritually dead live? Can the dry bones

00:18:27.360 --> 00:18:31.510
of the spiritually dead live? The

00:18:31.510 --> 00:18:31.520
seeker-friendlies,

00:18:31.520 --> 00:18:34.630
the lukewarm, can these

00:18:34.640 --> 00:18:38.549
bones live?'The Lord was saying again, as

00:18:38.559 --> 00:18:41.510
I could hear the sound of a mighty

00:18:41.520 --> 00:18:43.909
waterfall, just like

00:18:43.909 --> 00:18:43.919
when

00:18:43.919 --> 00:18:45.350
you hear rain in the

00:18:45.360 --> 00:18:48.950
distance and it's just

00:18:48.950 --> 00:18:48.960
pouring—you

00:18:48.960 --> 00:18:51.669
just hear it, I could hear it—and He

00:18:51.679 --> 00:18:54.150
said, 'The rain's coming. It's no longer

00:18:54.160 --> 00:18:58.470
coming, son; it's here.

00:18:58.480 --> 00:19:02.789
It's no longer coming, son; it's

00:19:02.789 --> 00:19:02.799
here.'That's

00:19:02.799 --> 00:19:04.630
what the Lord said. 'You'll start

00:19:04.640 --> 00:19:06.630
to see the first drops.'Even when it

00:19:06.640 --> 00:19:08.870
was with Charlie's funeral, his

00:19:08.880 --> 00:19:11.029
homegoing service, He said, 'You're

00:19:11.039 --> 00:19:14.390
seeing the first drops fall. You're

00:19:14.400 --> 00:19:17.909
seeing the first drops fall of a great

00:19:17.919 --> 00:19:21.350
outpouring of My Spirit upon all flesh.

00:19:21.360 --> 00:19:23.430
You're going to see what you never

00:19:23.440 --> 00:19:25.029
thought you—I mean, what you've always

00:19:25.039 --> 00:19:27.590
dreamed you would see.'But as I was

00:19:27.600 --> 00:19:29.909
looking,

00:19:29.919 --> 00:19:33.430
the Lord allowed me to see pressure.

00:19:33.440 --> 00:19:36.470
Persecution comes for His name's sake. I

00:19:36.480 --> 00:19:40.390
saw Canada. I saw the freedom to

00:19:40.400 --> 00:19:42.390
be able to say what you want to say.

00:19:42.400 --> 00:19:43.830
Even in our country, the First

00:19:43.840 --> 00:19:46.549
Amendment, the right to freedom of

00:19:46.559 --> 00:19:49.029
speech being challenged in the days

00:19:49.039 --> 00:19:51.510
ahead

00:19:51.520 --> 00:19:55.270
on social media platforms. But mainly in

00:19:55.280 --> 00:19:57.990
this vision, I saw it being challenged

00:19:58.000 --> 00:20:01.110
in Australia and in Canada.

00:20:01.120 --> 00:20:06.470
And I saw an olive press. And as the

00:20:06.480 --> 00:20:09.830
olive press was pressing the

00:20:09.840 --> 00:20:13.029
olives, I saw it being

00:20:13.039 --> 00:20:16.390
tightened and tightened and tightened.

00:20:16.400 --> 00:20:19.510
And as the olive press was pressing down

00:20:19.520 --> 00:20:22.870
upon the olives, it was springing forth

00:20:22.880 --> 00:20:25.669
beautiful olive oil. And this was

00:20:25.669 --> 00:20:25.679
a

00:20:25.679 --> 00:20:28.230
representation, I believe, of a new

00:20:28.240 --> 00:20:31.270
outpouring and a new

00:20:31.280 --> 00:20:34.470
pressure on

00:20:34.480 --> 00:20:38.310
the church. Out

00:20:38.320 --> 00:20:40.789
of the pressure

00:20:40.789 --> 00:20:40.799
of

00:20:40.799 --> 00:20:43.029
persecution

00:20:43.039 --> 00:20:48.310
came beautiful, fresh olive oil.

00:20:48.320 --> 00:20:52.549
I saw great darkness. I

00:20:52.559 --> 00:20:56.950
saw great trial for some,

00:20:56.960 --> 00:21:00.549
testing your faith, being persecuted for

00:21:00.559 --> 00:21:03.590
your faith in a way that

00:21:03.600 --> 00:21:07.110
this generation, a lot of Western

00:21:07.120 --> 00:21:09.590
society, would not be familiar with,

00:21:09.600 --> 00:21:13.110
compared to what maybe the Far East

00:21:13.110 --> 00:21:13.120
has

00:21:13.120 --> 00:21:16.870
experienced: a great persecution

00:21:16.880 --> 00:21:20.549
from China, from the

00:21:20.559 --> 00:21:23.350
Iron Curtain that's on North Korea, the

00:21:23.360 --> 00:21:26.070
darkness that tries to suppress

00:21:26.080 --> 00:21:28.070
Christianity all around the world, from

00:21:28.080 --> 00:21:31.430
Iranian Christians that are

00:21:31.440 --> 00:21:34.789
tortured and murdered

00:21:34.799 --> 00:21:39.590
without any kind of sympathy at all.

00:21:39.600 --> 00:21:43.270
And I saw that a lot of people think if

00:21:43.280 --> 00:21:45.990
they're persecuted in a comment

00:21:45.990 --> 00:21:46.000
section—which

00:21:46.000 --> 00:21:49.669
I have been in the past,

00:21:49.669 --> 00:21:49.679
and

00:21:49.679 --> 00:21:52.149
I don't even read

00:21:52.149 --> 00:21:52.159
them

00:21:52.159 --> 00:21:55.029
anymore—but

00:21:55.039 --> 00:21:58.070
through persecution, through these

00:21:58.080 --> 00:22:00.470
keyboard warriors,

00:22:00.480 --> 00:22:01.990
the Lord said that's not true

00:22:02.000 --> 00:22:04.230
persecution compared to

00:22:04.240 --> 00:22:05.909
when you're dragged down the

00:22:05.919 --> 00:22:08.230
street by a motorcycle driving down

00:22:08.240 --> 00:22:10.470
the street at 35 or 40 miles an hour and

00:22:10.480 --> 00:22:12.390
you're being dragged to death. That's

00:22:12.400 --> 00:22:14.549
great persecution, do you understand? Or

00:22:14.559 --> 00:22:16.310
losing your head for what you

00:22:16.320 --> 00:22:17.990
believe. That's persecution. That's

00:22:18.000 --> 00:22:19.990
martyrdom. And that's what the Lord was

00:22:20.000 --> 00:22:21.909
showing me: the Western culture

00:22:21.919 --> 00:22:23.350
doesn't understand that kind of

00:22:23.360 --> 00:22:25.029
persecution.

00:22:25.039 --> 00:22:28.070
But as your freedom of speech

00:22:28.080 --> 00:22:30.470
and other areas are tested in the

00:22:30.480 --> 00:22:33.029
days ahead, I saw great pressure coming

00:22:33.039 --> 00:22:38.070
from Canada upon the citizens

00:22:38.080 --> 00:22:41.270
in the days ahead. And I saw an olive

00:22:41.280 --> 00:22:43.430
pressing,

00:22:43.440 --> 00:22:46.310
and I saw the church

00:22:46.320 --> 00:22:50.710
going through a metamorphosis

00:22:50.720 --> 00:22:54.149
of growth spiritually.

00:22:54.159 --> 00:22:56.390
But as you take for granted the very

00:22:56.400 --> 00:22:58.789
freedoms that you have on a day-to-day

00:22:58.799 --> 00:23:01.990
basis, when that freedom is challenged

00:23:02.000 --> 00:23:04.549
and

00:23:04.559 --> 00:23:07.110
you're called to stand for

00:23:07.120 --> 00:23:10.390
something and make a choice, versus being

00:23:10.400 --> 00:23:14.149
a coward and hiding behind

00:23:14.149 --> 00:23:14.159
something—either

00:23:14.159 --> 00:23:16.390
you stand for something or you

00:23:16.400 --> 00:23:18.789
lose it.

00:23:18.799 --> 00:23:21.830
Either you get a backbone like a crowbar

00:23:21.840 --> 00:23:25.190
or you lose it.

00:23:25.200 --> 00:23:27.669
And the Lord showed me persecution

00:23:27.679 --> 00:23:30.630
coming upon the church in Europe,

00:23:30.640 --> 00:23:33.430
persecution coming to the churches

00:23:33.440 --> 00:23:38.149
because of people being lukewarm,

00:23:38.159 --> 00:23:41.830
not standing for what they believe,

00:23:41.830 --> 00:23:41.840
and

00:23:41.840 --> 00:23:43.909
taking things for granted.

00:23:45.760 --> 00:23:47.750
You will not be able to take for granted

00:23:47.760 --> 00:23:50.630
what you truly believe: pastors, great

00:23:50.640 --> 00:23:52.310
influencers.

00:23:52.320 --> 00:23:56.630
It was sad what I was seeing,

00:23:56.640 --> 00:23:59.270
but I saw a Holy Ghost church rise up

00:23:59.280 --> 00:24:04.070
out of their slumber.

00:24:04.080 --> 00:24:07.270
I saw a church rise up and say,

00:24:07.280 --> 00:24:09.909
'Enough's enough.'And they stood for

00:24:09.919 --> 00:24:11.990
what they believed in, and they weren't

00:24:11.990 --> 00:24:12.000
cowards

00:24:12.000 --> 00:24:14.710
anymore. It's kind of like Tommy

00:24:14.710 --> 00:24:14.720
Hicks'vision.

00:24:14.720 --> 00:24:17.510
If you go back to Tommy

00:24:17.510 --> 00:24:17.520
Hicks'vision

00:24:17.520 --> 00:24:21.269
and read

00:24:21.279 --> 00:24:23.990
about the glorious church, a giant in

00:24:24.000 --> 00:24:27.269
the land rises up because the

00:24:27.279 --> 00:24:30.070
Lord points the glory hand at

00:24:30.080 --> 00:24:32.950
him, and the giant rises up, and the body

00:24:32.960 --> 00:24:36.470
comes together and starts moving as one

00:24:36.480 --> 00:24:39.510
body instead of a bunch of rogue people

00:24:39.520 --> 00:24:42.630
like Rambo. The body comes together, and

00:24:42.640 --> 00:24:45.669
I told you what the Lord said to me, that

00:24:45.679 --> 00:24:48.630
you will see in the days ahead the body

00:24:48.640 --> 00:24:52.630
of Christ move as a body.

00:24:52.640 --> 00:24:55.350
It will no longer be, 'Well, you're

00:24:55.360 --> 00:24:57.990
Baptist, I'm Methodist, I'm Church of

00:24:58.000 --> 00:25:00.630
Christ, I'm Catholic, you're

00:25:00.630 --> 00:25:00.640
this.'No,

00:25:00.640 --> 00:25:04.630
it was a body joining together with

00:25:04.640 --> 00:25:07.669
one purpose and one cause, and that's to

00:25:07.679 --> 00:25:10.630
tell everybody that Jesus Christ is

00:25:10.640 --> 00:25:13.190
coming and it's time to repent and turn

00:25:13.200 --> 00:25:15.990
from your wicked ways.

00:25:16.000 --> 00:25:19.110
And I saw a glorious church rising. I

00:25:19.120 --> 00:25:21.990
saw a great revival coming from sea to

00:25:22.000 --> 00:25:25.190
shining sea all around this world. We're

00:25:25.200 --> 00:25:27.430
about to see the greatest harvest of

00:25:27.440 --> 00:25:30.070
souls this world has ever seen before.

00:25:30.080 --> 00:25:32.310
And we're going to see an outpouring of

00:25:32.320 --> 00:25:34.710
the Spirit of God like we've never seen

00:25:34.720 --> 00:25:36.870
before, and great

00:25:36.880 --> 00:25:39.029
manifestations and demonstrations of the

00:25:39.039 --> 00:25:41.830
glory.

00:25:41.840 --> 00:25:45.190
But it will come when the church—I saw a

00:25:45.200 --> 00:25:47.110
great shaking is what I'm trying to tell

00:25:47.120 --> 00:25:55.430
you. I saw a great shaking to awaken,

00:25:55.440 --> 00:25:58.470
and the church starts to wake up, and the

00:25:58.480 --> 00:26:01.830
giant takes form.

00:26:01.840 --> 00:26:04.789
And there's brush harbor churches. I saw

00:26:04.799 --> 00:26:08.070
the old tent

00:26:08.070 --> 00:26:08.080
revivals

00:26:08.080 --> 00:26:10.149
coming back.

00:26:10.159 --> 00:26:12.789
I saw, like Mario Murillo, you know, he

00:26:12.799 --> 00:26:15.590
does these tent meetings, I saw tent

00:26:15.600 --> 00:26:18.230
meetings coming back and

00:26:18.230 --> 00:26:18.240
a

